title: WANDAVISION EPISODE 3 BREAKDOWN! Easter Eggs & Details You Missed! (1x03 "Now In Color")
author: New Rockstars
description:
WandaVision 1x03 full episode shot-by-shot analysis! What is the deeper MCU secret in the HYDRA SOAK commercial, and what was Herb about to say when he said: "She came here because we're all..."? Visit http://helixsleep.com/rockstars for up to $200 off your mattress.

Watch the NEWEST videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL4xEo4XxrSJbbjsGMSWDN62z8XB6QzHFy

WandaVisionâ€™s third episode, "Now In Color," jumps ahead to the 70s, in a Brady Bunch themed episode that featured creepy reality glitches, references to Quicksilver and Ultron, and Wanda's new children Billy and Tommy, aka the mutants and Young Avengers Wiccan and Speed in the Marvel comics. How does the Hydra soap connect to a similar simulated reality episode of Agents of SHIELD, and what does that tell us about the mission of SWORD, the off-shoot of SHIELD now monitoring Wanda and Westview? Erik Voss breaks down all the deeper Easter Eggs and hidden details that you missed in this episode of WandaVision, Season 1 Episode 3.
